OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774004767
OL,3,COfficials to face questions after
OL,4,Cstudents turned away from meningitis
OL,5,Cjab queue
OL,7,FThe University of Kent said it had
OL,8,Fclosed the vaccine queue on its
OL,9,FCanterbury campus "due to capacity" on
OL,10,FThursday because it needed to finish
OL,11,Fthe clinic by 5pm.
OL,13,FMore than 100 people who had been
OL,14,Fwaiting for a jab were turned away,
OL,15,Faccording to Press Association
OL,16,Festimates of the queue size.
OL,18,FThe university said the vaccination
OL,19,Fclinic will reopen on Friday from 9am
OL,20,Fto 5pm, and advised people to be in
OL,21,Fthe queue by 2pm.
OL,26,@qD@SOUqD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
