CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774004767
OL,3,COfficials to face questions after
OL,4,Cstudents turned away from meningitis
OL,5,Cjab queue
OL,7,FMore vaccination centres are also due
OL,8,Fto open across Kent as the
OL,9,FGovernment's immunisation programme
OL,10,Fexpands.
OL,12,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said
OL,13,Fanyone who attended local venue Club
OL,14,FChemistry from March 5 until March 15
OL,15,Fwould be offered the jab, alongside
OL,16,Fsixth-formers at four schools and
OL,17,Fother university students in
OL,18,FCanterbury.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
