PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774004767
OL,3,COfficials to face questions after
OL,4,Cstudents turned away from meningitis
OL,5,Cjab queue
OL,7,FOne facility, located at Faversham
OL,8,FHealth Centre, will begin
OL,9,Fadministering jabs at 9am on Friday
OL,10,Fand will remain open through Saturday,
OL,11,Fwhile additional clinics are scheduled
OL,12,Fto open on Friday at the Vicarage Lane
OL,13,FClinic in Ashford and at the
OL,14,FUniversity of Kent, NHS England has
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,18,Fsaid that as of 5pm on Wednesday, 15
OL,19,Fcases of meningitis have been
OL,20,Fconfirmed and a further 12 are under
OL,21,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
