PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774004767
OL,3,COfficials to face questions after
OL,4,Cstudents turned away from meningitis
OL,5,Cjab queue
OL,7,FThis takes the total to 27 cases of
OL,8,Feither confirmed or suspected
OL,9,Fmeningitis, up from 20 on Wednesday.
OL,10,FTwo students have died in the outbreak.
OL,12,FCurrently, nine of the 15 confirmed
OL,13,Fcases are known to be caused by menB.
OL,15,FThe UKHSA said all patients eligible
OL,16,Ffor antibiotics will now be able to
OL,17,Frequest a vaccination and antibiotics
OL,18,F"from their local GP immediately `
OL,19,Fwherever they are in England". This
OL,20,Fcovers students who have travelled
OL,21,Fhome.
OL,26,@zD@AOU{D@]O]
